Launch ec2 instance.
Click on launch instance.
Give a proper name to it.
Select ami and key.
Create security group ssh 22,port 80 and another port custom TCP 8081 and click on launch instance.
It will launch instance.
Take ssh and go in the instance.
Install update(sudo yum update).
Install nginx service(sudo yum install nginx).
Start nginx service(sudo systemctl start nginx).
Enable nginx service(sudo systemctl enable nginx).
Check nginx service is working or not on browser.
Take public ip of instance and run on browser.
Change listen in configuration file.
Change directory /etc/nginx(cd /etc/nginx/ ).
Edit configuration file with the help of editor.
Open configuration file(sudo vim nginx.conf).
Update listen [8081].
Save this file.
Restart nginx service(sudo systemctl restart nginx).
Run on browser public ip (port :8081).
